 Victoria Beckham, 48, posted a shot of herself hugging husband David Beckham from behind as they took a ride on a jet-ski.  It comes as the couple have been holidaying on their luxury yacht, stopping off at various countries around Europe.  In the latest pictures, the pair were off the coast of Italy as they bravely took to the waters in their swim wear with both of them wearing essential life vests.  In view of her 30.2 million Instagram followers, the mother-of-four captioned the sunny snap: "Yes, that’s right… @davidbeckham got me on a jet ski. What next?!"  The couple appeared in good spirits with David donning a pair of shades and Victoria opting for a sporty black cap. 